---
import PromoStrip from '@components/PromoStrip.astro';
import StickyMobileCTA from '@components/StickyMobileCTA.astro';

const { title, description } = Astro.props;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="el">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description} />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans text-gray-800 antialiased pb-24 md:pb-0">
  <PromoStrip />
  
  <header class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-gray-100/50 sticky top-0 z-40 shadow-sm transition-all">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-allpower-obsidian">
        Power<span class="text-allpower-accent">Station</span> Hub
      </a>
      <a href="https://iallpowers.eu/?ref=Allpowers-compact-energy&utm_source=aff" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600 hover:text-allpower-accent transition-colors hidden sm:block">
        Official Partner Offers
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <slot />
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-allpower-dark text-gray-400 py-10 text-center text-sm border-t-4 border-allpower-accent">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="mb-4">Είμαστε επίσημος affiliate συνεργάτης της ALLPOWERS. Όλες οι αγορές γίνονται με ασφάλεια στο επίσημο site της ALLPOWERS Europe.</p>
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} PowerStation Hub | Independent Affiliate Project</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <StickyMobileCTA />
</body>
</html>
